query:
SELECT p.id, s.name as service, c.name as country, p.smshubPrice as cost, p.ourPrice as price, 
ROUND((p.ourPrice - p.smshubPrice) / p.smshubPrice * 100, 2) as calculated_profit
FROM prices p
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id
WHERE s.name LIKE '%Outros%' AND p.apiId = 2;
